@startuml sie-homeostasis-seq-002-actuate-remediation-v1

' ============================================================
' VISUAL THEME
' ============================================================

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam ArrowColor #57606A
skinparam DefaultFontName "SansSerif"
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF

skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF8C5
skinparam noteBorderColor #57606A

title SIE Governance Sequence - Homeostasis - Actuate Remediation - v1

autonumber

participant "Description Plane - EVAL-HOM-TRG-001" as EFF_HOM_TRG_001
participant "Definition Plane - R-HOM-001" as R_HOM_001
participant "Definition Plane - OP-HOM-001" as OP_HOM_001
participant "Remediation Plane - EFF-HOM-002" as EFF_HOM_002
participant "Remediation Plane - R-HOM-REMED-002" as R_HOM_REMED_002
participant "State Plane - EFF-HOM-FB-001" as EFF_HOM_FB_001
participant "Definition Plane - R-HOM-002" as R_HOM_002

EFF_HOM_TRG_001 -> R_HOM_001 : [INT-HOM-TRG-001] ControlIntentEvent(phase=ACTUATE)
note over OP_HOM_001
  Executes BR-HOM-001 controlSequence
  - BRC-HOM-002 Actuation Gate + Dispatch
end note
EFF_HOM_002 -> R_HOM_REMED_002 : [INT-HOM-002] ActuationControlEvent
note over EFF_HOM_FB_001, R_HOM_002
  Operational feedback is observed in State
  and re-enters via Description -> Definition receptors.
end note
EFF_HOM_FB_001 -> R_HOM_002 : [INT-HOM-FB-001] ActuationFeedbackEvent

@enduml
